<h2><b><u>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</b></u></h2>

<h3>Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</h3>

<h4><b><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></b></h4>

<h4><b>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</b></h4>
<h4><b>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</b></h4>
